data.description: Bring the whole family! Great price with a defined Mother in Law Suite!  Don’t miss out…. A beautiful move in ready home awaits you! This 5 bedroom , 3 full baths, home offers all the luxury and space for the entire family! Includes a full in-law suite, large eat in kitchen with pantry, primary room has on-suite with separate shower and bath, tray ceiling w/9x14 walk in closet, two large main living areas, formal dining area, laundry room, 4 large bedrooms, attached 3 car garage with an oversized parking pad, 9x19 screened in lanai and partially fenced in backyard. This house sits on a large landscaped corner lot, in a sought out gated community. A perfect home sweet home to call your own!
